    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Class for keeping statistics of a continuously sampled process / signal. Useful if the storage of individual samples is not necessary or desired. Also useful if the number of samples is not known beforehand or exceeds available memory. </para>    </detaileddescription>
